-Place-Home-Whistler-Burgers-Architecture-20.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\" data-cfsrc=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Cypress-Place-Home-Whistler-Burgers-Architecture-20-810x540.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=564879\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-564879\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Cypress-Place-Home-Whistler-Burgers-Architecture-21-810x594.jpg\" alt=\"A modern house with large glass windows and a sloped roof is surrounded by snow and tall trees under a twilight sky. The interior lighting gives the house a warm glow.\" width=\"810\" height=\"594\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Cypress-Place-Home-Whistler-Burgers-Architecture-21-810x594.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Cypress-Place-Home-Whistler-Burgers-Architecture-21-800x586.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Cypress-Place-Home-Whistler-Burgers-Architecture-21-768x563.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Cypress-Place-Home-Whistler-Burgers-Architecture-21.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\" data-cfsrc=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Cypress-Place-Home-Whistler-Burgers-Architecture-21-810x594.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=564880\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-564880\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Cypress-Place-Home-Whistler-Burgers-Architecture-22-810x651.jpg\" alt=\"A modern, snow-covered house with large glass windows and a steep roof, surrounded by pine trees during twilight.\" width=\"810\" height=\"651\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Cypress-Place-Home-Whistler-Burgers-Architecture-22-810x651.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Cypress-Place-Home-Whistler-Burgers-Architecture-22-800x643.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Cypress-Place-Home-Whistler-Burgers-Architecture-22-768x617.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Cypress-Place-Home-Whistler-Burgers-Architecture-22.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\" data-cfsrc=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Cypress-Place-Home-Whistler-Burgers-Architecture-22-810x651.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eFor more information on Burgers Architecture, visit \u003ca href=\"https://burgersarchitecture.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener external noreferrer\" data-wpel-link=\"external\"\u003eburgersarchitecture.com\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cem\u003ePhotography by \u003ca href=\"https://www.instagram.com/emaphotographi/?hl=en\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener external noreferrer\" data-wpel-link=\"external\"\u003eEma Peter Photography\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n                        \n                                                    \u003cdiv\u003e\n                                \u003cdiv\u003e\n                                    \u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2021/11/Caroline-Williamson-100x100.jpg\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2021/11/Caroline-Williamson.jpg 2x\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" alt=\"\" data-cfsrc=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2021/11/Caroline-Williamson-100x100.jpg\"/\u003e                                    \u003c/p\u003e\n                                \u003c/div\u003e\n\n                                \u003cdiv\u003e\n                                    \u003cp\u003eCaroline Williamson is Editor-in-Chief of Design Milk. She has a BFA in photography from SCAD and can usually be found searching for vintage wares, doing New York Times crossword puzzles in pen, or reworking playlists on Spotify.\u003c/p\u